channel.title: Not letting people on my server no more
channel.description: Hi, i turned off my laptop... then turned it back on because it was lagged... now it's not letting me host my server at all... i suppose it could be about the exeptions thing, but whenever i try to add MOPAR or NO-IP it still doesnt work? am i getting it wrong? or what? please help :D
